= Deepali Adlakha---Industry Experience

== Facebook

=== Video Monetization, Core App Monetization

Manager: Zhuowei Bao\n
Location: Menlo Park

- Team's mission is to build monetization products to fund the livelihoods of a thriving Facebook video creator ecosystem
- Currently working as the Tech Lead on Advertiser Demand for Ad Breaks
- Ad Breaks enables creators to monetize video watching experience on Facebook. We build controls to help advertisers place their ads inside videos on Facebook
- Key projects that I have been working on - enabling advertisers to use our product, developing infrastructure for advertisers to control where their ads are placed and improving their buying experience


=== Brand Solutions, Ads and Businesses

Manager: Brian Rosenthal\n
Location: London

- Team's mission is to support brand advertisers on Facebook. Brand advertisers aim to improve their brand value through Facebook ads as opposed to expecting people to respond directly to their ads
- Key projects that I worked on were - Offline Conversions and Creative Hub
- Offline Conversions helped advertisers target ads based on people's offline purchases
- Creative Hub enabled creative agencies to create and play with mock ads before publishing their clients' ads on Facebook
